dct_title_s: Amplissimae regionis Mississipi seu provinciae Ludovicianae â R.P. Ludovico Hennepin Francisc. Miss. in America Septentrionali anno 1687 detectae, nunc Gallorum Coloniis et actionum negotiis toto orbe celeberrimae, nova tabula
dct_description_sm: Shows the United States west to New Mexico, parts of Canada and Mexico, and routes of various explorers to 1716. Relief shown pictorially. "Cum privilegio Sac. Cæs. Maj." Some text in French. Includes views of Niagara Falls, Father Louis Hennepin and the Buffalo. Has insignae of Ins. Gall. Societatis Indiae Occidentalis.
